  "body": "Can you call setState() from within a ref callback?  The answer is \"Yes\".  (Though it's probably not a good idea).\n\nIt's really confusing what is permitted / good / bad / illegal.  Especially because different things are legal at different times in the lifecycles.  Even if something is legal, it might be a bad idea.  We should clarify.\n",
